# 🔁 TASK LIFECYCLE

Every task follows:

1. CREATED (client submits)
2. QUEUED (backend stores)
3. RUNNING (worker active)
4. PLANNING (Claude)
5. IMPLEMENTING (GPT)
6. REVIEWING (Claude)
7. COMPLETED
8. FAILED (with logs)

